description: Help space for those with diabetes
overview: Healthy Humans develops powerful yet user-friendly e-portal health solutions designed to improve health outcomes while lowering costs. The Healthy Humans team of leading medical doctors and enterprise software developers created Health eHub, a patient-empowering medical home platform that provides continuity care and enhanced care-coordination to improve the quality of care that physicians can provide to their patients.
